=head1 DESCRIPTION

A structure that represents a valid record field header and whether it
is mandatory.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Mandatory => Bool

If this is C<true>, the record field must be present in the
C<recordFields> parameter provided to a CreateDelivery
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonCloudWatchLogs/latest/APIReference/API_CreateDelivery.html)
or UpdateDeliveryConfiguration
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonCloudWatchLogs/latest/APIReference/API_UpdateDeliveryConfiguration.html)
operation.


=head2 Name => Str

The name to use when specifying this record field in a CreateDelivery
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonCloudWatchLogs/latest/APIReference/API_CreateDelivery.html)
or UpdateDeliveryConfiguration
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonCloudWatchLogs/latest/APIReference/API_UpdateDeliveryConfiguration.html)
operation.



